reviewText: Great!  My little boy loved the VBS and loves the DVD!
Our Awana kids love the music! Very well done, and I didn't even get paid to say this :)
Love Love Love it! I am so glad we finally found this dvd for purchase.
all our vbs students (kids and adults loved it).  really loved the interactive  aspect of the dvd.  got everybody up, on their feet/out of their seats and excited.
